al operators and problems of new kind for equations with\nsolutions of arbitrary growth at singularity.\n  The Russian original paper version is also included, it is slightly different\nfrom english one.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Apr 2013 06:41:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-03"}
